20 there is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 As used in this act:
22 1. "Emergency action plan" or "EAP" means a written, site-
23 specific plan addressing preparedness response, evacuation,
24 sheltering, and communication for severe weather hazards;
ENGR. H. B. NO. 1675 Page 1

